t can be decomposed under unitary similarities into\nvarious $k$-dimensional block-diagonal forms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2020 19:36:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2020 14:46:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-20"}
