irst-principles results. The two levels exhibit\nclose features, conforming to a model where the electronic character of\n$\\mathrm{C_{i}O_{2i}}$ can be described by that of $\\mathrm{C_{i}O_{i}}$\nperturbed by a nearby O atom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 08:03:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-03"}
