_{n,n-1})$ by a simple combinatorial property. In\nparticular, the short exact sequence allows us to determine a new and efficient\npurely combinatorial representation of elements of\n$\\mathrm{Aut}(X_n^{\\mathbb{N}}, \\sigma_{n})$, and we demonstrate how to compute\nproducts using this new representation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 09:10:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 31 Oct 2021 19:07:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-02"}
