ary conditions for our modified ADM\nsystem, as well as for the hyperbolic system used in the propagation of the\nconstraints. An additional analytical difficulty arises from a loss of control\non the normal derivatives to the boundary of the solution. To resolve this\nissue, we work with an anisotropic scale of Sobolev spaces and exploit the\nspecific structure of the equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 09:56:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 12:36:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
