 experiments\nwhich show that the CAE encodes more phonetic, word duration, language identity\nand speaker information than the other multilingual models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 12:28:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 08:03:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-08"}
